# FF Orbit MCP Architecture

Orbit is snapshot-first.
- Snapshot: local point-in-time project files.
- Index: symbols/edges extracted from snapshot.
- Changeset: draft edits + preview + validation + apply.

Core tool signature:
```ts
orbit({ cmd: string, args?: object, snapshot?: string, format?: "json"|"explain" })
```

Primary command groups:
- Discovery: `projects.list`, `snapshots.create`, `snapshots.refresh`, `snapshots.info`, `snapshots.ls`
- Query: `pages.list`, `page.get`, `widgets.list`, `widget.get`, `search`, `summarize.*`
- Edit: `page.create`, `page.update`, `page.delete`, `widget.create`, `widget.set`, `widget.delete`
- Safety: `changeset.preview`, `changeset.validate`, `changeset.apply`, `changeset.drop`

Prefer deterministic commands over exploratory probing.
